# 🎓 Student Data Organizer

A menu-driven Python application to manage student records using Lists, Dictionaries, Tuples, and Sets.

## 🚀 Features

- Add Student
- Display All Students
- Update Student Information
- Delete Student Record
- Display Unique Subjects Offered
- Exit Program

## 🛠 Concepts Used

- List
- Dictionary
- Tuple
- Set
- Functions
- Loops
- Conditional Statements

## 📂 Data Stored

Each student record contains:

- Student ID
- Name
- Age
- Grade
- Date of Birth
- Subjects

## ▶️ How to Run

```bash
python student_data_organizer.py
```

## 📸 Sample Output

```text
1. Add Student
2. Display Students
3. Update Student
4. Delete Student
5. Display Subjects
6. Exit
```

